Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petra, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going in to get looked at today no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you are wasting your time, no \N matter how often you come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I'm coming all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody called for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stubborn, pigheaded woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who is talking, you quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not seen a doctor once since I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but as you can see, I am doing just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, we have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Schumann!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is that drunkard, Fink!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hit on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is he conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who carried him in is treating him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who was just passing by is examining Fink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told him you were out on a house call, he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You allowed that person to treat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to stop him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he said the patient might choke, so I \N had to let him give first aid, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left without giving his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he did write something on the chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The patient said not to take him to a \N doctor because he had no money..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...so please use this to pay for his medical fees."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was Asian, and he had a boy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... what about Mr. Fink's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that man only too emergency measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were not emergency measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.82,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(283,0)\pos(322,323)}Petra and Schumann
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't follow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go to school like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who wasted your time at my clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware that Fink is just a penniless drunkard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even considered taking money from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are probably some elite doctor \N from a famous hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...showing mercy during your vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and having a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is work?  Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me when I am talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we are in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fink was involved in a hit and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lush?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm looking for witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Fink's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I am worried about his drinking problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is Dr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was my junior at my old college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is visiting this village because he is on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He treated Fink for me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while I was off making a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you know where I went today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see your mother, Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell her to come to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may need to treat her immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stubborn woman won't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that like it doesn't concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been watching over me this long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she has anything left to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only just begun to live her own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For saving Fink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without your swift treatment, he would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned white as a sheet when \N you saw the policeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.  Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least now I'm sure you are not an elite \N doctor from a famous hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I can repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A debt, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll ask you to pay some of it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!  Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cast is a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might hurt a bit, but bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!  Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to take it off in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Doctor, I got some nice apple brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An injured man should not be thinking of such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be back on the farm in five more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Mr Schöne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, please take some potatoes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very tasty this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll come by in my truck next \N time and fill it to the brim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My area of expertise is internal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm doing my best in areas outside my expertise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't take care of everything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Even though there is nothing \N here, it is a peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are loved by the people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you really love them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost such admirable feelings long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, help me with one more place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I'll keep coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how many times you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and get lost, you quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the mother of that policeman you met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she suddenly felt sick during her farm work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to take her to a clinic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she said she felt on the way there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and went back home by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to try to convince her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might turn out the same, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still dawdling about out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I dawdle is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep yelling like that, nobody \N would want to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you to a clinic no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose my reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I just meant that I don't want to lose \N the person I love to argue with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Also, I would not be able to eat the goulash she makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You face is really red, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say, you brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the door, Ms. Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Another doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stubborn woman is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They mess around with people's bodies \N thinking they are gods or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times I wish I were a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we try our best...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mistakes will always happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could heal people perfectly, like god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart hesitates every time I examine a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, at least show us your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are making goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You like goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it looks like Dr. Shumann only likes your goulash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I have heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I made it for him, he just sat and ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is very shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, my shoulders ache so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have to prepare dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoulders ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Petra, can you touch your chest with your chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fit four fingers in...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of charm was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a subarachnoidal hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received this fax regarding the \N search for a murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me some copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your mom okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she collapsed three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't die, even if you kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,72 hours since her first spasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is borderline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to operate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they will make it in time, even \N if we call for a helicopter right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can operate on her, do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll lose another loved one, and it will be my fault again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure he was Kenzou Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, he could not have gotten very far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put up roadblocks on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a great achievement if we catch him, Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All officers, emergency deployment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes well, I'll get a promotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heinz.  You have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Heinz here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi, Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom collapsed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had forced her to check into \N a hospital after the first spasm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my only hope, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an aneurysm in the fork of the middle cerebral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have a surgical microscope \N or craniotome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have cerebral artery clips, I'll try operating \N on her without a microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that will be difficult, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If her cerebral aneurysm ruptures again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm afraid she might not make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is happening again, and it is all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong, Dr. Schumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not acting like someone who has taken \N care of an entire village single handedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in the past, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we must work our hardest for the patient before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all doctors can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Dr. Schumann inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he is operating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operating?  On my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did not bother taking her to a city \N clinic... he is operating on her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood pressure and pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood pressure, 126/84.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even have a craniotome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he opened her skull this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, we are operating on your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you are doing with that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put you hands up, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are in the middle of surgery here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill your own mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who is trying to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is running around the \N country suspected of murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has already killed a man in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is also a suspect for the serial murder \N of several middle aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would find you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is giving me a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry and put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sterile operating room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are bringing in germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If infection enters this room, your mother could contract \N meningitis, and her life would be at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and stop the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really trying to kill your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is suffering from a \N subarachnoidal hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She first collapsed three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't treat her now, it will be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you have a hostage or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are thinking of taking my mother hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and getting out of this situation, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cerebral artery clips and forceps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cerebral artery clips and forceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who hurts my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right, Petra is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done for your mom these past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you even gone to see her since \N you moved out to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done for your mother \N in return for her raising you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People you cherish will disappear someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember the taste of your mother's goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, Petra makes your share out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end up eating your share as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing else like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is fighting vigorously right \N now, trying to save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to taste that goulash again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then just get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?  Everything is okay, thanks to Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood pressure, 140/86.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse, 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her vital signs are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get some rest, Ms. Pionere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Go get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I will take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get some sleep as well, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in that difficult operation \N for several hours straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better safe than sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that once Ms. Petra's all better, \N you can propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "propose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought you were asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I take that guy in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, what did he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not someone who can propose to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was working in a university hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I felt that talking to my patients was secondary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was more concerned with how to \N solidify my position in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sided with the director's political faction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote the director's thesis for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I got permission to marry the director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I just kept marching \N down the promotion highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not even look at my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had looked at my wife, I would have noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been a real doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, my wife had been plagued by \N symptoms similar to that of the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had paid more attention to her, I would have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was liver failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally... looked at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked at them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked at everyone in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Petra was saved because you looked at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to take this man in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still think he is a murderer, after he \N gave his all trying to save your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call off the roadblocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I saw wasn't Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mistook him because he is Asian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, sir.  Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doctor from the national hospital was very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably never thought to see such splendid medical \N treatment from a clinic out here in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are gonna let that young doctor go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would treat him to something \N tasty, but he already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This village is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Schumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter, you like it here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This village might be good for Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can protect you from the police \N if you stay in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of the people here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This village needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Dieter for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!  I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, we can save numerous lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save numerous lives...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to kill a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not capable of such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You work so hard to save the lives of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is going...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma will go no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are with him, he won't stray from his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Tenma carefully.
